<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SBR WALK 2025 - Replay</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --blue-bg: #6b8fa6; /* The dusty blue from your images */
            --dark-blue: #3d5666;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif; /* Matching the elegant serif style in your images */
            background-color: var(--blue-bg);
            color: var(--white);
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* --- SHARED LAYOUT --- */
        section {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-around;
            padding: 0 8%;
            position: relative;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .content-left {
            max-width: 500px;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .image-right img {
            max-width: 450px;
            height: auto;
        }

        h2 { font-style: italic; font-weight: normal; font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        p { line-height: 1.6; font-size: 1.1rem; opacity: 0.9; font-family: sans-serif; }

        /* --- HEADER & MENU --- */
        .hamburger {
            position: fixed;
            top: 30px;
            right: 40px;
            border: 1px solid var(--white);
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        /* --- SECTION SPECIFICS --- */
        #home { 
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4), rgba(0,0,0,0.4)), 
                        url('https://img.freepik.com/free-photo/wood-material-background-wallpaper-texture-concept_53876-42925.jpg?w=740');
            background-size: cover;
        }

        .reg-link { color: var(--white); text-decoration: underline; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px; display: block; }

        /* --- BOTTOM NAV PILL (Matches images) --- */
        nav {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 40px;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .logo-small {
            background: var(--glass);
            border: 1px solid var(--white);
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
        }

        .nav-pill {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border: 1px solid var(--white);
            padding: 10px 30px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            align-items: center;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .nav-pill a { 
            color: var(--white); 
            text-decoration: none; 
            font-size: 0.8rem; 
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-family: sans-serif;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .nav-pill span { color: gold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="hamburger">||</div>

    <section id="home">
        <div class="content-left">
            <h1 style="font-size: 4rem; font-style: italic; margin: 0;">SBR WALK</h1>
            <p>SBR Walk's 9th iteration! ☀️<br>"REPLAY: Trip Down Memory Lane" 🎞️</p>
            <a href="#registration" style="background: var(--purple); color: white; padding: 12px 25px; border-radius: 50px; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; background: #3d2b56;">⚡ REGISTRATION</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about">
        <div class="content-left">
            <h2>Yearly Event of Sekolah Bogor Raya</h2>
            <p>
                SBRWALK is an annual event organized by Sekolah Bogor Raya to promote community involvement and fundraising. 
                The website has been created since 2016, and had been including activities such as yoga, running, and even bands. 
                The last year's event...
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="image-right">
            <img src="YOUR_LOGO_HERE.png" alt="SBR Walk Logo Replay">
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="registration" style="background-color: #5d7c91;">
        <div class="content-left">
            <h2>Registration! Get your slots!!</h2>
            <p>
                The last year's event, SBR WALK 2025: "Replay" with the tagline: Trip Down Memory Lane. 
                Last year's event was about reminiscent of the past because it coincided with the SBR's 30th anniversary.
            </p>
            <p>To register the event, go to the link below. The deadline of the registration is 18th July 2025:</p>
            <a href="#" class="reg-link">Registration Link: ——————</a>
        </div>
        <div class="image-right">
            <img src="YOUR_LOGO_HERE.png" alt="SBR Walk Logo Replay">
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="bookcall">
        <div class="content-left">
            <h2>Yearly Event of Sekolah Bogor Raya</h2>
            <p>If you have any confusions or questions...</p>
            <h3 style="font-family: sans-serif; margin-top: 20px;">Call: +62-7439-8394-711</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="image-right">
            <img src="YOUR_LOGO_HERE.png" alt="SBR Walk Logo Replay">
        </div>
    </section>

    <nav>
        <div class="logo-small">⚡</div>
        <div class="nav-pill">
            <a href="#home">Home</a> <span>➔</span>
            <a href="#about">About</a> <span>➔</span>
            <a href="#registration">Registration</a> <span>➔</span>
            <a href="#bookcall">Book Call</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

</body>
</html>